             sworn. - I took the prisoner into custody for the handkerchiefs, but nothing was found on him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I never saw the boy at all; I was going to my aunt's the same day.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18020428-143-verdict737" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020428-143-verdict737" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 14.</p>
               <p>Of the larceny.</p>
